":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"661eaae3fb9c11090144f88bac782ebf4722779a","tid":1468360,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:36:44.000Z","msg":"你老母就做得唔啱<br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師屌前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:07.000Z","msg":"一樣還一樣 <br />\n打狗救手足我覺得一啲問題都冇<br />\n問題係阻住救護救人我地一定冇咁嘅權力<br />\n我地同班狗唔同架"},{"pid":"38769f57440a0e73bfc93bcef61172ca1384656d","tid":1468360,"uid":41636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2faf4d62b3e9fa52a0e4d64c0794b07251e3139","tid":1468360,"uid":41636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:54.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b26a3d40a11a1cee8c6d6c72e4d16cbb38cd569c","tid":1468360,"uid":41636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:05.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"09ba5ddc7bc323d4728f6bbb6bd4f76199c388c0","tid":1468360,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:09.000Z","msg":"不需要　完美得可怕<br />\n有ＢＵＧ好正常"},{"pid":"789f575b657d64b6f119c1ac5cb5c715b9a2a4f7","tid":1468360,"uid":139365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c71c1914c1ec19d30007c321efeefbfd35ea4ae4","tid":1468360,"uid":41636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:15.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9c849241c7339018769f4c7fdba4c1805fcdac9b","tid":1468360,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不割蓆，唯要改進</span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔會割蓆，但我地亦都會持續去改進，希望運動可以更上一層樓邁向成功之日，我地要一齊尊重，正如人人平等冇話邊個大啲有得話事啲，我地亦要每日一齊去檢討得失，正如人人都會有失誤<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動其中一樣重要嘅係自己要有一個自省精神，出現失誤就要認，認完就要反省，下次再可以做好啲，人數亦會keep住多，人多就可以贏<br />\n<br />\n如果出現失誤唔去承認，唔去反省，只會繼續重蹈覆轍，人數會變少，最後重演2014年雨革失敗歷史"},{"pid":"8d333105e59a4bc055364b52ef71b787cecb11bf","tid":1468360,"uid":68096,"li